    <p>Montana Commissioner of Securities and Insurance (CSI) data shows non-renewal and premium increase complaints concentrated in Missoula, Ravalli, Gallatin, and Flathead counties. Rural Bitterroot Valley communities report some of the thinnest admitted-market options in the state.</p>
